io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.MediaLibrary

  • Packages that use MediaLibrary 
    Package Description
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary
    All classes within the MinecraftMediaLibrary.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.dependency
    Dependency management classes relating to installation, relocation, and loading into the global classpath can be found here.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame
    Advanced functions such as dithering, VLC C++ interaction can be found here.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.chat
    Classes used to display videos in chat.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.entity
    Classes used to display videos in entity clouds.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.gif
    Classes used to display gifs.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.highlight  
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.map
    Classes used to display videos onto maps.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.parallel
    Classes used to display videos in chat.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.scoreboard
    Classes used to display videos in scoreboards.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.image.basic
    Classes relating to static imagery.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.image.gif
    Classes relating to dynamic imagery.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.listener
    A set of listeners used by the library to unregister/register players.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.logger
    A built in logger function for MinecraftMediaLibrary only itself to avoid console spam and also allow better debugging details.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.resourcepack
    A set of resourcepack wrapper utilities and checks to wrap a resourcepack very easily.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.utility
    A set of utility classes used throughout the MinecraftMediaLibrary framework.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.vlc
    Testing classes to test the VLC media player.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.vlc.os
    Special Operating System dependent solutions for installing VLC.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.vlc.os.linux
    Linux Implementation.

    Special Linux Distribution dependent solutions for installing VLC.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.vlc.os.mac
    Mac Implementation.
    io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.vlc.os.windows
